\newlabel{tab:pareto}{{1}{6}{\textbf {Our full method dominates the compute-vs-elicitation Pareto frontier; baselines and ablations do not.} Headline comparison across all method variants on the main-comparison slice. The final column marks each method as Pareto-optimal or dominated; only \emph {Ours: full} sits on the frontier at the high-compute end. A scatter version of this table will replace it in a later draft}{table.caption.1}{}}
